STATE
v.
Robert Lee HOLMES. No. 641P06. Supreme Court of North Carolina. March 8, 2007. Allison Corum, Derrick C. Mertz, Assistant Attorney Generals, Garland N. Yates, District Attorney, for State.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 8th day of February 2007 by Defendant to Strike State's Response:

"Motion Dismissed as moot by order of the Court in conference this the 8th day of March 2007."
